show.description: Dev Joshi, stuck in a contract marriage, devotes himself to Rati Kapoor, who never values him. Her heart remains with her first love, Avinash, aided by her scheming siblings Pooja and Prem. After Rati dismissively signs divorce papers, Dev leaves and rebuilds his life into a billionaire researcher. He finds true respect and affection with Shreya Rao, unlike the humiliation he endured with Rati. In the end, Dev rejects Rati’s late realization and chooses a dignified future with Shreya. Watch now.
